Hi <%= @golfer.partner_name %>,

<%= @golfer.name %> has registered you as their playing partner for <%= @tournament.name %>.

<% formatted_date = @tournament.event_date.is_a?(Date) ? @tournament.event_date.strftime('%B %-d, %Y') : (begin; Date.parse(@tournament.event_date.to_s).strftime('%B %-d, %Y'); rescue; @tournament.event_date || 'TBA'; end) %>
Event: <%= formatted_date %> | <%= @tournament.location_name %><%= ", #{@tournament.location_address}" if @tournament.location_address.present? %>

<% if @is_swipe_simple %>Payment is being handled by your team captain. You're all set!<% end %>

<% if @tournament.tournament_info.present? %>

Tournament Info:
<%= @tournament.tournament_info %>
<% end %>

Questions? Contact <%= @tournament.contact_name.presence || 'us' %><%= " at #{@tournament.contact_phone}" if @tournament.contact_phone.present? %><%= " or #{@tournament.contact_email}" if @tournament.respond_to?(:contact_email) && @tournament.contact_email.present? %>.

See you on the course!
<%= @org_name %>
